RES (TSV)","guid":"ZxX-c8XLQCiO2EcMtXDLfA","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"Taquicardia por reentrada nodal (TRNAV) → MAS FRECUENTE","guid":"6_ItZN8vS2apIVFtLiBX0w","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"Taquicardia por via accesoria (TRAV)","guid":"EIMeJQVaQ4i8-kgqJSOnMw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"Taquicardia auricular","guid":"mQVS_DsiR3OwURVNIY5l0Q","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"Manejo escalonado","guid":"UqWSHVRIRSKb9YU_CZzJkA","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Maniobras vagales → primer paso","guid":"yUO4vxzRS_mEhN0JOCFrXg","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Valsalva modificado (mayor tasa de exito)","guid":"nj5X-Do5RUGliTLJKIvf0A","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Masaje carotideo (precaucion en AM → soplo?)","guid":"r5C-1ajcSHCFGIc7mVQa2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"Adenosina IV","guid":"yxhLXjOPRmK1ESb57LUSKQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"6 mg IV push rapido + flush","guid":"J0Zx55bcRIOc8a7yJ8ddFw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Si no responde → 12 mg IV","guid":"ykLVhF2kTtCMKXBRkVcuxQ","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"Vida media ultracorta (6-10 seg)","guid":"9q6dFiVnSF6NO3ec2NpjEg","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"Contraindicada en asma severa, WPW conocido","guid":"cQM9I3ZeS1WyqDipHpo0WA","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"172","text":"Verapamilo 2.5-5 mg IV o diltiazem","guid":"7M9G3md1SC2cfjTbf78Rsw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"172","text":"Cardioversion sincronizada si refractaria o inestable","guid":"LXQx29XqRHydwVTaNhJplw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"TAQUICARDIAS VENTRICULARES (TV)","guid":"OnUwbTE7Te2FkgLT_aih_Q","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Clasificacion","guid":"TXFfICGJSMa1HosIIm5xDA","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"TV MONOMORFA → QRS uniforme","guid":"TMY9srLtRnqgX41oJciXDg","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Sostenida (>30 seg o inestabilidad)","guid":"HtwAMNeyQGauCX2zS6wOYQ","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"No sostenida (<30 seg, autolimitada)","guid":"5JYb2K8yRDquVLs5B8qRAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"TV POLIMORFA → QRS variable","guid":"gZosyywnTjWgq779Rx3YVA","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Con QT normal → isquemia hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"YMcKToNoQ2CxvGZ4UzzXRQ","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Con QT largo → Torsade de Pointes","guid":"PtypMtYDRgix-uxdXVEDsA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"183","text":"Manejo TV monomorfa sostenida","guid":"3Pi6vkPCRqiLZQZU-Dc3Lg","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"INESTABLE → cardioversion sincronizada 100-200 J","guid":"cGWLZ9u8SkOfWHbVPS189Q","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"ESTABLE → farmacologico","guid":"DCdJsDCvREyJ-YFFyNTTXA","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"NNT TheNNT → Procainamida vs Amiodarona en TV estable","guid":"XtHXGOHFSlquF7-mW0uRvQ","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"Estudio PROCAMIO (Ortiz 2017, Eur Heart J)","guid":"qhuPnRrORmW2L9Q1L9yAzg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"74 pacientes con TV estable","guid":"_rvrK-LGQQmddtMDopZfWA","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"194","text":"Procainamida 10 mg/kg IV en 20 min","guid":"G5kKcLcuRLeuQbJWIDjQBw","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"194","text":"NNT 4 para conversion a ritmo basal","guid":"-FIPSp6LSNOlDwld_MDnNw","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"194","text":"NNH 3 para eventos adversos cardiacos mayores con amiodarona","guid":"bczjq3M6Rpm9gTTl3fBCYw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"194","text":"Recomendacion AMARILLA → evidencia debil pero mejor disponible","guid":"wZ_bYRVlTvSM0fcVAnQAcw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"194","text":"AHA recomienda procainamida (IIa) sobre amiodarona (IIb)","guid":"daIVX8oHTE6UQedn6uou-A","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"194","text":"PERLA → procainamida superior a amiodarona en TV estable","guid":"qY7YCu9wRw28vk0Bamgz9g","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"193","text":"Amiodarona 150 mg IV en 10 min → alternativa","guid":"S56l6TghSASGwXPBcl5pOA","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"Luego infusion 1 mg/min x 6h → 0.5 mg/min x 18h","guid":"i8B8p0vrSv-bZTlKZytnhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"193","text":"Lidocaina → rol limitado actualmente","guid":"cB0rQEeKR_ade16LM5fT3A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"183","text":"Torsade de Pointes","guid":"GIrOeu4VQByDW92pMOdyTQ","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"QT largo + TV polimorfa","guid":"MkUfVThdQ7S58cGlGtqP2w","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"Causas → farmacos (antiarritmicos IA/III, macrolidos, antipsicóticos), hipoK, hipoMg","guid":"PCOJu0dvSkGDEPETWlwGaA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"Manejo → MgSO4 2 g IV en 2 min (primera linea)","guid":"VGecFkXyRd6DBV5WMXRyZw","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"Isoproterenol o marcapaso temporal (overdrive pacing)","guid":"964u4OQkSruMqps8s-knJg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"206","text":"Cardioversion si inestable","guid":"HngokRVSQN-hrcZPBhhSpQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"206","text":"NO dar amiodarona (prolonga QT)","guid":"7jnbavdlSzC9ngslIhJf2Q","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"206","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → causa frecuente: polifarmacia con farmacos que prolongan QT","guid":"M38SE2G4SK61FOdAZ39FZw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"0","text":"BRADIARRITMIAS","guid":"WeY2XYpEThqINcpo0wyKFQ","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Bradicardia sinusal","guid":"jJgfVo5STfWpkvGt37ip4A","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"FC <60, puede ser fisiologica","guid":"MM-ywEObQMelqVsKkis7Ow","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"Sintomatica si hipotension, sincope, IC","guid":"OvtZhDlpRomri4-6otT-VQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"Bloqueo AV","guid":"M64bgl13SRG29VPEU-Oa8g","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"1er grado → PR >200 ms, benigno","guid":"EjBrF8umT9GBx_ggGBItZA","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"2do grado Mobitz I (Wenckebach) → generalmente benigno","guid":"o6oXvL72RvyglbFzFev3yQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"2do grado Mobitz II → riesgo de progresion, considerar marcapaso","guid":"6HhW4yy0T5OWqT-Needd5g","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"218","text":"3er grado (completo) → emergencia, marcapaso","guid":"_Su9uu1kTy2SVg62-Mi8vg","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"214","text":"Manejo bradicardia sintomatica","guid":"CuB-3CgIT4-VL1APhmmMWw","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"Atropina 0.5-1 mg IV (puede repetir hasta 3 mg)","guid":"TOtWJ7E_TAC8Z37DSFbHxQ","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Inefectiva en BAV 3er grado infranodal","guid":"mOSEkO7XRl2rAY7IYjDbbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"223","text":"Isoproterenol infusion 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"rtGgKLk0T3CMBWc-NI2pWA","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"223","text":"Dopamina 5-20 mcg/kg/min","guid":"QQswWhJhQkKI3-hp1ZAlhQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"223","text":"Adrenalina 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"mdgSWoTjRTGgXmaHFlVtLQ","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"223","text":"Marcapaso transcutaneo → puente a transvenoso","guid":"oz2QS4xmRfCHXxFauR3lCQ","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"223","text":"Marcapaso transvenoso temporal → definitivo","guid":"-0s09zPWTcmh_hSVoxn-kg","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"214","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"QR256GuMQTuVHXf96QxjOg","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"Bradicardia frecuente por farmacos (betabloqueadores, digoxina, calcioantagonistas)","guid":"2awfhqhORUafxCLPej9qlA","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"Enfermedad del nodo sinusal","guid":"Bb3qlylBTIOPBcZ3McCPTg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"Degeneracion del sistema de conduccion","guid":"sU7X5JhkREqrDCGHjYtoCg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"PERLA → siempre revisar farmacos antes de asumir bradicardia intrinseca","guid":"UXWe3tamSaWyqe6zFogZjQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIATRICAS TRANSVERSALES","guid":"WYFS5O03TCSyyrVQNdhzDw","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"Farmacocinetica alterada","guid":"cBdFUUDeQf6Yutv9AoEJhw","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"Menor metabolismo hepatico → acumulacion amiodarona","guid":"xdXdKq85TwiKAme8c54Mww","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"237","text":"Menor filtracion glomerular → ajustar digoxina, DOACs","guid":"PHIwgSxtSX--ujA90WhrHw","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"237","text":"Mayor sensibilidad a farmacos cronotropos negativos","guid":"wBEqjS8GS8OVlQKrYeKoWg","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"237","text":"Menor masa muscular → creatinina falsamente normal","guid":"gITZ3cOeQRiw1mwIo85yxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"236","text":"Comorbilidades","guid":"B0a1b17oSh-N8ewLRc9l6g","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"IC + FA → combinacion frecuente en AM","guid":"CbuQh4LuR8GMpQHGxNAzHA","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"ERC → ajustar anticoagulacion","guid":"lwVPPCD5RF-p-gh9L-l7rQ","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"Caidas → evaluar riesgo antes de anticoagular (HAS-BLED no es razon para no ACO)","guid":"J6Eh6XMbSomJt5I7VDUHbw","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"242","text":"Fragilidad → individualizar metas","guid":"Yeo1_mnGR2eKNbTbhwA8FQ","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"242","text":"Demencia → adherencia farmacologica comprometida","guid":"50Oh_2oQTnma_c_g1nJmWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"236","text":"Polifarmacia","guid":"RgZlSwYuTuySZOYS_y8s5A","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"Interacciones con anticoagulantes","guid":"tKEpyrEWSuC7zmkvV84mgA","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"Farmacos que prolongan QT → lista larga en AM","guid":"N01brJdZQQ6sQyGvASf_AA","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"Antipsicóticos, antidepresivos, macrolidos, quinolonas, ondansetron","guid":"0y2vNP0SQ3GKVTxvLRekRQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"248","text":"Carga anticolinergica de algunos antiarritmicos","guid":"350mzWY4T1iOyFK4uiL00Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"236","text":"Decisiones de proporcionalidad","guid":"iRxA7PdXQEq_tbxbkV_8kw","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"FA permanente en AM muy fragil → solo control FC, no anticoagular si riesgo > beneficio","guid":"uVzkLZSQQsOvm9v760SpIQ","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"Considerar directivas anticipadas","guid":"DmNom2rjSIqVO4jOfqtNqw","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"253","text":"Calidad de vida sobre longevidad en decisiones","guid":"9ZsMtAT7SjCDaJ0ac4GDyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO RESUMEN FA EN URGENCIA","guid":"NW68S6skS9W7K2vuj0rgaA","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"PASO 1 → Confirmar FA (ECG) + evaluar estabilidad","guid":"klNEkhkSTtutIk0Ul0q4Bg","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"PASO 2 → Inestable → cardioversion electrica sincronizada","guid":"wO1HPSKAQBC-ab8co2rInw","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"PASO 3 → Estable → control de frecuencia (betabloqueador o calcioantagonista)","guid":"pHvOhBgYSZ2gEkv8VokTPA","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"PASO 4 → Buscar causa (infeccion, IC, TEP, tiroides, electrolitos)","guid":"IjEX60arSxSPeCaV8y90dg","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"257","text":"PASO 5 → Evaluar necesidad de cardioversion vs mantener control FC","guid":"U0IclOt-QqiX-hG0fFqmbg","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"257","text":"PASO 6 → Anticoagulacion segun CHA2DS2-VASc","guid":"23vayRCYRHin6GlBgMwa7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO RESUMEN TAQUICARDIA QRS ANCHO","guid":"tPhArXMCSamUVL4Zm2mm4g","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"Regular + monomorfa → TV monomorfa → procainamida o cardioversion","guid":"Y_vhVO8GRgaotlOTC4RuRw","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"Regular + polimorfa + QT largo → Torsade → MgSO4","guid":"c4zS2xPRQ7yJUj9au7-X4Q","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"264","text":"Irregular + QRS ancho → FA preexcitada (WPW) → procainamida o cardioversion, NO frenadores NAV","guid":"pXwFnCaPRNirXm9CArivvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"0","text":"LR DIAGNOSTICOS","guid":"s-EovJbnQkW8O8hLIZM87w","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"HALLAZGOS CLINICOS (cabecera)","guid":"DFa8PjBtR1G9EB2HjAIPbg","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"Pulso irregularmente irregular (palpacion medica) -> LR+ 4.5 -> LR- 0.16 -> PMID:16536961","guid":"mmMWvcfXQriyDHArjAmPaw","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"Auscultacion cardiaca irregular -> LR+ 4.2 -> LR- 0.2 -> PMID:17673732 (SAFE)","guid":"n4xAP1YDQGyLSO8DqBoHFA","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"Pulso irregular detectado por paciente -> LR+ 1.9 -> LR- NR -> PMID:16536961","guid":"SpPRQgJiRGyhBa6OZSLV0A","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"269","text":"Deficit de pulso (apical > radial) -> [descriptivo clasico, LR no consolidado]","guid":"FqVcbdQKQQuWMPZ1-n3X4Q","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"269","text":"Palpitaciones + mareo -> sintoma comun, no LR especifico","guid":"g_Q7Q3oOTtiGk4xRao4OYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"268","text":"HALLAZGOS ECG","guid":"HXSugxlFRHCi1ApnqXfaNA","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"ECG 12 derivaciones (gold standard) -> LR+ muy alto -> (definitorio)","guid":"kS3qVwpQTyO9vuWgZQfctw","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"Ausencia de onda P + R-R irregular -> [definitorio FA]","guid":"YwBY4cc-R22YMwOreJru9A","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"Taquicardia irregular QRS angosto -> FA vs taquicardia atrial multifocal","guid":"lktxJy4gT1eh8uvviZ7BUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"279","parent":"268","text":"DISPOSITIVOS","guid":"p8P9FODSST-9dLOqLR6yAQ","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"Single-lead ECG (AliveCor, Apple Watch, KardiaMobile) -> LR+ ~30-100 -> LR- ~0.02 -> PMID:24687081","guid":"IA0anVLAT0GMOrQslfXooQ","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"279","text":"Oximetria de pulso con deteccion FA -> LR+ 8.4 -> LR- 0.2 -> PMID:29562087","guid":"goNhc57rRZmiuBsp_Bu7CA","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"279","text":"Holter 24-48h (FA paroxistica) -> variable por duracion monitoreo","guid":"h-3T3VrsSF2nhAj8YCZHbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"268","text":"SCORE / REGLA CLINICA (riesgo embolico)","guid":"2oqZDMxjR3q-f4EArA-GpA","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"CHA2DS2-VASc >=2 (hombres) o >=3 (mujeres) -> indicacion anticoagulacion","guid":"uZovIIsGSxGKhWk7IkcoLw","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"283","text":"HAS-BLED >=3 -> alto riesgo sangrado, no contraindica AC sino intensifica monitoreo","guid":"Xl5dnSL4TSWb9h6p9NJKwA","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"283","text":"EHRA >=IIa -> indicacion control ritmo","guid":"Q0lpQGZnTEWCQ6TxN1HYqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"268","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"N2oeAZ7tTOKTcz4xygRM6w","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"LR+ >10 o LR- <0.1 -> cambio GRANDE (single-lead ECG con algoritmo)","guid":"EnxvAV1_SrKY1o06PTS1SQ","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"LR+ 2-5 -> cambio moderado (palpacion pulso irregular)","guid":"lreYDkdoQvGreNZHKqGR-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"268","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"iUc48idbTMqwBS_IaV1QGw","children":[{"id":"291","parent":"290","text":"Prevalencia >10 porciento en >80 anos","guid":"IJ_j0XfbRtqUwQqFC22NRw","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"290","text":"Fragilidad y riesgo de caidas NO son contraindicaciones absolutas a anticoagulacion","guid":"Z91AHurtTHaKcLblH3_Vww","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"290","text":"Ajuste DOACs por edad, peso, creatinina (Apixaban criterios 2/3: >=80a, <=60kg, Cr >=1.5)","guid":"H4rHGeF6RM6dZ5quYvTA0Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"0","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"QgT-DKtTSe-WieQTap3Znw","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"ESC 2024 → guia manejo FA","guid":"NkdRw5fRQ4SITj3RLkXziQ","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"RACE II → control lenient vs estricto (Van Gelder 2010, PMID:20231232)","guid":"7WIiw08ISYq_q8RvhXhcsg","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"PROCAMIO → procainamida vs amiodarona en TV estable (Ortiz 2017, PMID:28025219)","guid":"WnEXXa1ESGeScWRkxRkavw","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"294","text":"ARISTOTLE → apixaban vs warfarina en FA (Granger 2011, PMID:21870978)","guid":"cONprVcMSNK5WNCfVKLogw","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"294","text":"RE-LY → dabigatran vs warfarina (Connolly 2009, PMID:19717844)","guid":"Qf3ImcBwRhygqPUilK3ZFw","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"294","text":"AFFIRM → ritmo vs frecuencia en FA (Wyse 2002, PMID:12466507)","guid":"zLOQd_5CTBOlChoA3mVXIw","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"294","text":"TheNNT.com → NNT de MgSO4 IV en FA+RVR, procainamida vs amiodarona en TV","guid":"lk9xrEm0TTa5xDa_pFQwNQ","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"294","text":"Kirchhof 2016 → ESC guidelines AF (PMID:27567408)","guid":"yIU9KxV7QtORmKZsC6NyCw","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"294","text":"January 2014 → AHA/ACC guideline AF (PMID:24682347)","guid":"Y9M08o2kRaehgeGJLEi-jQ","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":303,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"MUE - Medicina de Urgencia","filename":"MUE_FA_Arritmias","id":"map_2506","resolved_references":[]}